{"tid":565534,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"無波靚樣中女 和 大波平凡樣輕熟女，點取捨？","createTime":"2018-02-19T05:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T08:25:02.000Z","uid":38539,"like":13,"dislike":170,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbbd65eccc75ad9a04d0c03d510183429f9d9d3","tid":565534,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:18:26.000Z","msg":"先搞清楚定位<br />\n<br />\n中女 - 廣義上，指所有踏入中年的女性，而香港一般見解指中年為三十到四十九歲。<br />\n輕熟女 - 輕熟女族群泛指年紀25歲至35歲之間，擁有獨立的經濟能力的都會女性。<br />\n<br />\n設定如下<br />\n<br />\n中女 - 靚女，但係無波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n輕熟女 - 大波，但係樣子普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038cb1db0c1a040319c228d3ab64266f1fe3367b","tid":565534,"uid":22624,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"一大遮三醜"},{"pid":"e15a447be48fe97beb3ec6213f384250b8530ebd","tid":565534,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"樣可以化妝<br />\n波就算隆咗都只係中看不中用"},{"pid":"c80e71e9c855dde251f5bd3880698c8ef45984b2","tid":565534,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"輕熟女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3422adb613a6c6da638c16af958f7315d9f9c0","tid":565534,"uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":65,"score":-63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"以下圖片做例子 (純粹以外表角度判斷，特意打咗黑線，等你哋認唔出乜水)<br />\n<br />\n中女代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/132054_f66533e57036b598f535b7683dc4c75a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F132054_f66533e57036b598f535b7683dc4c75a.jpg&h=04953c55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輕熟女代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/132102_ce735c56384385eb0e9a1e928a90e387.j